== Biography

I'm a MPhil student at the [http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk Department of Computer Science and Engineering],  
[http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/english/index.html The Chinese University of Hong Kong (CUHK)], 
under the supervision of [http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~byu/ Prof. Bei Yu] since Fall 2026.
Previously, I received my Bachelor degree from The Chinese University of Hong Kong in 2026.

My research interests include LLM and AI4EDA.



